{"tid":1977491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"龍門逆市開沙田分店　月租20萬較舊舖貴45%","createTime":"2020-04-18T04:25:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T17:38:39.000Z","uid":256095,"like":16,"dislike":163,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"7cbbef9b72055d8d1eadb8f2cd5ef32f7c6c89b0","tid":1977491,"uid":256095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:25:58.000Z","msg":"一直高調支持反修例的「黃店」龍門冰室逆市擴張，最新以20萬元租用沙田河畔花園地舖，為繼租用尖沙咀金龍中心舖後的第7間分店。<br />\n<br />\n結合市場消息及土地註冊處資料顯示，該舖位於沙田河畔花園地下19至20號商舖，面積約1,700方呎，每月租金20萬元，呎租約117元。店舖前租戶為長和（0001）旗下屈臣氏，每月租金約13.8萬元，換言之，是次龍門冰室的租金較屈臣氏高出45%。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以上係3月份嘅新聞<br />\n明知疫症好多黃店小店做唔住<br />\n點解佢仲可以開舖 分薄小店生意？<br />\n佢就賺到盤滿缽滿<br />\n仲要高價同人租舖勁闊佬<br />\n其他小店就告急執笠</span></span>"},{"pid":"4da963f66099862dbd159438d6c7b63fecdbc7dc","tid":1977491,"uid":21545,"like":77,"dislike":2,"score":75,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:27:46.000Z","msg":"做生意唔可以賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ffdf4f60ef10b0d48b37eb8d004860deeb2b071","tid":1977491,"uid":245534,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:28:06.000Z","msg":"P牌分化撚"},{"pid":"572e38187657d4192d60f1f5fe5d53580568a261","tid":1977491,"uid":323373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:28:23.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"14849d80cc749975dec29195d6020845ba206e74","tid":1977491,"uid":43369,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:28:59.000Z","msg":"最好開到m記咁"},{"pid":"78923e3a82ca85dc108d284435e0d0f6693f6368","tid":1977491,"uid":353267,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:29:02.000Z","msg":"之前唔係有一間黃店野飲喺龍門對面 龍門就日日排長龍 啲人為咗打卡<br />\n跟住對面間鋪就冇人啦 汁左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36648f0e437b591768f7dfff62d844627b9fb2b6","tid":1977491,"uid":353267,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:29:50.000Z","msg":