9</a>"},{"pid":"c99f5a9b54e1ca557ade7c9d89c374cfb8d1dbae","tid":1977491,"uid":349976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:51:31.000Z","msg":"講埋啲咁嘅說話，一睇就知樓豬未做過生意。"},{"pid":"25de90b5983a84b6b6fa8da86adf46fafc556366","tid":1977491,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:51:41.000Z","msg":"你啲分化手段太低裝啦，係咪好撚驚黃店愈做愈大？"},{"pid":"a2aec4916897efec1f246f686d2b8573b4de8678","tid":1977491,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:52:32.000Z","msg":"怪唔知得俾人追擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3f5b638dc0cc9c0dd77e3df73d769a462c2121","tid":1977491,"uid":109428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:54:29.000Z","msg":"你老母個墓頭市價幾多？"},{"pid":"6603732e271182c8ce46598ca9d55b0903f2f836","tid":1977491,"uid":74935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:55:15.000Z","msg":"關你撚事P牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfffb5928aff59ff57643f35c167fb5d6839aa65","tid":1977491,"uid":43984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57b4f1fa93e7fb5d3d32184712deb75a382859f7","tid":1977491,"uid":298115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"14849d80cc749975dec29195d6020845ba206e74","tid":1977491,"uid":43369,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:28:59.000Z","msg":"最好開到m記咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:50:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:56:43.000Z","msg":"有黃色連鎖店幾好"},{"pid":"22c98b1b36de98d5249a8445d85966b429c9f2ac","tid":1977491,"uid":146656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:57:05.000Z","msg":"五毛分化blocked 拉"},{"pid":"53177ad3b6053ca637e837967e00d2f46db1d6d8","tid":1977491,"uid":235140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:57:13.000Z","msg":"最好區區都有分店，多啲選擇"},{"pid":"5e32c16c9c546f66418462394c5ec2097